@828  = ~He carries intrigue upon his person like a well worn cloak, that much is certain, but attraction?~
@829  = ~I do not believe Tsujatha to be capable of anything that is not serious, my raven.~
@830  = ~Ah. 'Tis a risky venture you propose, for the both of us mayhap.~
@831  = ~Is it true he was your brother's ally? I do believe that adds much credibility to the notion that anything can be bought. But what of him, my raven?~
@832  = ~If, hypothetically, I was perhaps interested in pursuing Angelo... what would that mean for you and I?~
