@836  = ~Truly? This sparrow would say that seems an odd match, but stranger pairs have existed and thrived, I suppose.~
@837  = ~Then perhaps you should not torment the man with hope, hmm?~
@838  = ~'Tis a surprise to this sparrow, but it seems you speak truth.~
@839  = ~I suppose that depends upon what exactly you'd like me to do.~
@840  = ~Ah, our poetic refugee from the Underdark. What of him?~
