@872  = ~Then you are cruel to him, and naught but pain will result from such games.~
@873  = ~It does seem so, aye.~
@874  = ~I do not think the paladin will respond well to such games, my hound.~
@875  = ~The sellsword with the unique tongue and roving eye? Aye, what of him?~
